== Rouge application 

Rails app developed following the instructions of 'Using JRuby - Bringing Ruby to Java' book.

This is a awesome book, highly recommended for anyone interested in JRuby world.

== Modifications on the original application

- Use of MySQL JDBC Connector with 'activerecord-jdbc-adapter' gem.
Download it here: http://www.mysql.com/downloads/connector/j/
After downloading, copy the .jar into /lib folder of the rails app.

- Developed 'java_jar_dependencies.rb' initializer to load the java application dependencies, located at /lib folder.

